snippet.title: Top 10 Hits: Amber
snippet.description:
Marie-Claire "Amber" Cremers (born 17 September 1969) is a Dutch-born German singer, songwriter, label owner, and executive producer. 
Between 1996 to 2006 she scored in the U.S. charts 5 Top-100 hits and 12 Top-10 hits in Billboard's Dance/Club chart which 5 of them peaked at No'1.
Her debut hit 'This is Your Night' peaked at No'1 in Israel,No'3 in Spain No'11 in Australia, No'14 in The Netherlands and No'24 on U.S. Top-100.
In December 2016, Billboard ranked her as the 34th most successful dance artist of all-time.
